metadata.name: Max Verstappen in colors
metadata.description:
The speed of Formula 1 is amazing. I have just a little bit colorized it!

Max Verstappen is F1 world champion after beating Lewis Hamilton to the chequered flag on the last lap of the season finale in Abu Dhabi!

The winning bid will also receive this image as a physical print signed by the author, shipped worldwide. Contact me @safronovf1 after the auction has ended.

3508 × 3508 // 300 dpi //  12 Mb
